      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained vehicle for your daily drives? This car is in good condition, offering a smooth ride and a clean interior that shows it's been well-cared for over the years! It\u2019s a dependable choice that\u2019s ready to hit the road with confidence and style.",
