    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention. The engine currently runs but produces a persistent knocking sound and has multiple active fluid leaks. The transmission is prone to slipping between gears, and there is visible rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells. This car is recommended for a buyer looking for a project or for parts, as it is being sold strictly as-is with no guarantees of roadworthiness.",
